    <example xml:id="ex_no_limit2">
      <title>The Function Grows Without Bound</title>
      <statement>
        <p>
          Explore why <m>\lim\limits_{x\to 1} 1/(x-1)^2</m> does not exist.
        </p>
      </statement>
      <solution>
        <p>
          A graph and table of <m>f(x) = 1/(x-1)^2</m> are given in <xref ref="fig_nolimit2">Figure</xref> and <xref ref="table_nolimit2">Table</xref>, respectively. Both show that as <m>x</m> approaches <m>1</m>, <m>f(x)</m> grows larger and larger.
        </p>
        <sidebyside widths="47% 47%">
          <figure xml:id="fig_nolimit2">
